<div class="columnOne">
    <div class="innerContent">
        <h1>Supporting policymakers and practitioners across the UK</h1>
<p>Building on four decades of experience, The Knowledge Exchange provides knowledge services to local authorities, public agencies, research consultancies and commercial organisations across the UK. We provide:</p>
<ul>
<li>the most comprehensive database of UK public policy and research available - the Idox Information Service;</li>
<li>on-demand enquiry and research services;</li>
<li>intelligence news and briefings across planning, health, social care, education and more.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="/consultancy/">Learn more about our services here</a></strong></p>
    </div>
